HEADWORD: Carabid
<hw>Car"a*bid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or resembling, the genus <gen>Carabus</gen> or
family <fam>Carabidae</fam>.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>One of
the <fam>Carabidae</fam>, a family of active insectivorous
beetles.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

